name: Seal, Staff Officer of the Skyfang Brigade
desc: During your Main Phase: You can Special Summon 1 "Skyfang Brigade" monster from your hand, except "Seal, Staff Officer of the Skyfang Brigade". If another "Skyfang Brigade" monster(s) is Special Summoned to your field while this monster is on the field: You can target 1 "Skyfang Brigade" monster in your GY; add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Seal, Staff Officer of the Skyfang Brigade" once per turn.
